button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 06, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zvw1767356556880.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zvw1767356556880.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zvw1767356556880.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zvw1767356556880\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The layout template system provides a centralized mechanism for generating consistent\n\t\tinitial HTML content—including &lt;head&gt; sections, scripts, and document structure—for\n\t\tDSP applications. This allows common elements to be managed in one location while individual\n\t\tDSPs contribute their specific content.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">For more information on how to use the layout template system in DSP components, see\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dfo1767602589534.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dfo1767602589534.html\" title=\"The Layout Mode property is a component-level setting that determines how a DSP’s layout content is processed during HTML generation. It controls the interaction between custom HTML and the layout template system.\">Layout Mode Property</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"boz1767604932735.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/boz1767604932735.html\" title=\"The layout template system provides a centralized mechanism for controlling the HTML structure of DSP applications. When a DSP request is processed, USYSHTTP invokes DSP.HANDLER-&gt;genResponse(), which calls the USYSHTTP_LAYOUT::GETHTMLLAYOUT global ProcScript library to generate the final HTML output.\">Customizing Layout Template</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dfo1767602589534.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Layout Mode Property</a><p>The Layout Mode property is a component-level setting that determines how a DSP’s layout content is processed during HTML generation. It controls the interaction between custom HTML and the layout template system.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/boz1767604932735.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Customizing Layout Template</a><p>The layout template system provides a centralized mechanism for controlling the HTML structure of DSP applications. When a DSP request is processed, USYSHTTP invokes DSP.HANDLER-&gt;genResponse(), which calls the USYSHTTP_LAYOUT::GETHTMLLAYOUT global ProcScript library to generate the final HTML output.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_27055950\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_27055950\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Layout Template System Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 06, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The layout template system provides a centralized mechanism for generating consistent initial HTML content—including <head> sections, scripts, and document structure—for DSP applications. This allows common elements to be managed in one location while individual DSPs contribute their specific content. For more information on how to use the layout template system in DSP components, see Layout Mode Property and Customizing Layout Template . Related Links Layout Mode Property The Layout Mode property is a component-level setting that determines how a DSP’s layout content is processed during HTML generation. It controls the interaction between custom HTML and the layout template system. Customizing Layout Template The layout template system provides a centralized mechanism for controlling the HTML structure of DSP applications. When a DSP request is processed, USYSHTTP invokes DSP.HANDLER->genResponse(), which calls the USYSHTTP_LAYOUT::GETHTMLLAYOUT global ProcScript library to generate the final HTML output. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}